{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770989134,"nonce":"usWFm9OMQHIutiXuCSjBHfmTReU=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOQ241x87qrJ4P","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/195","origin":"github"},"title":"fix: detect_agent_identity.sh reports stale model name (Opus 4.5 instead of 4.6)","message":"## Problem\n\n`detect_agent_identity.sh` relies on hardcoded model defaults in `framework_config.sh`. The Claude entry currently says `Claude Opus 4.5`, but the actual runtime model is now `Claude Opus 4.6`. This causes:\n\n- `env.sh` reports `Model: Claude Opus 4.5` at session start\n- `set_git_identity_env.sh` sets `AGENT_MODEL=Claude Opus 4.5` (wrong)\n- When run outside the workspace context, falls back to `Unknown Model`\n- Git commit metadata and identity signatures carry stale model names\n\n### Affected files\n\n- `.agent/scripts/framework_config.sh` — hardcoded `FRAMEWORK_MODELS` table\n- `.agent/scripts/detect_agent_identity.sh` — `detect_actual_model()` checks `$CLAUDE_MODEL` env var but Claude Code doesn't set it\n\n### Current detection logic (claude case)\n\n```bash\nif [ -n \"$CLAUDE_MODEL\" ]; then\n    detected_model=\"$CLAUDE_MODEL\"\nelse\n    detected_model=\"${FRAMEWORK_MODELS[claude]}\"\nfi\n```\n\n`$CLAUDE_MODEL` is never set by the Claude Code runtime, so it always falls through to the hardcoded default.\n\n## Proposed fix\n\n1. **Update `framework_config.sh`** — change default to `Claude Opus 4.6`\n2. **Improve runtime detection** — investigate whether Claude Code exposes the model name via any environment variable, config file, or API that the script could read at startup instead of relying on a hardcoded string\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- `env.sh` reports the correct model at session start\n- `AGENT_MODEL` env var matches the actual runtime model\n- The fix is forward-compatible (doesn't break when the model changes again)\n\n---\n**Authored-By**: `Claude Code Agent`\n**Model**: `Claude Opus 4.6`","files":null}]}